    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Privateers, or pirates, active along the coast of the Barbary States. Saracen and Turkish corsairs were authorized to loot ships and settlements under Christian rule.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
